据报道 GAME 工作人员被告知要裁员https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/game-staff-reportedly-told-to-expect-redundancies-3615320?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=game-staff-reportedly-told-to-expect-裁员Issy van der VeldeTue, 09 Apr 2024 10:19:41 +0000 Gaming NewsNewsVideo Game Culture https://www.nme.com/?p=3615320 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Game-storefront-UK.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="曼彻斯特特拉福德中心的 GAME 店面" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Game-storefront-UK.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Game-storefront-UK-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Game-storefront-UK-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Game-storefront-UK-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Game-storefront-UK-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Game-storefront-UK-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>目前尚不清楚有多少人会受到影响</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/game-staff-reportedly-told-to-expect-redundancies-3615320">据报道，GAME 工作人员被告知预计裁员的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Game-storefront-UK.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="曼彻斯特特拉福德中心的 GAME 店面" decoding="async" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Game-storefront-UK.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Game-storefront-UK-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Game-storefront-UK-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Game-storefront-UK-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Game-storefront-UK-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Game-storefront-UK-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道，英国视频游戏零售商 GAME 的员工被告知要裁员，因为大多数员工都转为零工时合同。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/tv-interviews/twisted-metal-star-stephanie-beatriz-quiet-interview-3613729">《扭曲金属》明星斯蒂芬妮·贝翠丝：“我忘了我必须记住台词！”</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://www.eurogamer.net/game-staff-told-to-expect-redundancies-as-most-workers-move-to-zero-hours-contracts" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Eurogamer</em></a>报道，多名 GAME 员工匿名向该网站透露，并确认大多数非管理人员现在将采用零时合同。他们还补充说，这并不意外。</p><p>据报道，受裁员影响的 GAME 员工将通过电话或电子邮件得知，但目前尚不清楚有多少人会受到影响。 <a href="https://www.ladbible.com/entertainment/gaming/game-store-closing-uk-shop-340758-20231229" target="_blank" rel="noopener">多家游戏商店于 2023 年 12 月关闭</a>，目前尚不清楚这些裁员是否意味着更多游戏商店会效仿。 <em>《NME》</em>已联系星狮集团请其置评。</p><p>过去几年，GAME 的许多高街商店都关门了，转而转向 Sports Direct 和 House of Fraser 商店内的特许摊位。星狮集团于 2019 年以 5200 万英镑收购了 GAME。 </p><figure id="attachment_2815944" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2815944" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-2815944" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Shop-Credit-Convery-Flowers-Alamy-Stock-Photo@2000x1270.jpg" alt="游戏店" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Shop-Credit-Convery-Flowers-Alamy-Stock-Photo@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Shop-Credit-Convery-Flowers-Alamy-Stock-Photo@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Shop-Credit-Convery-Flowers-Alamy-Stock-Photo@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Shop-Credit-Convery-Flowers-Alamy-Stock-Photo@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Shop-Credit-Convery-Flowers-Alamy-Stock-Photo@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Game-Shop-Credit-Convery-Flowers-Alamy-Stock-Photo@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2815944" class="wp-caption-text">图片来源：Convery Flowers / Alamy Stock Photo</figcaption></figure><p>今年2月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/game-stores-to-stop-all-trade-ins-from-next-week-3585155">游戏商店宣布停止所有旧游戏的以旧换新</a>。许多英国孩子都曾在 GAME 上用旧游戏换取新的、打折的二手游戏。不幸的是，商店也将停止销售二手游戏和游戏机。</p><p>这一消息遵循了数字销售超越物理媒体的最新行业趋势。到 2022 年，北美销售的所有游戏中有 60% 是数字游戏。数字化的便利性不容忽视，但数字店面不会永远持续下去， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/nintendo-closing-wii-u-and-3ds-eshops-in-2023-3163379">任天堂 3DS 和 Wii U 数字商店的关闭表明了这一点</a>。随着游戏变得越来越昂贵，二手市场帮助许多玩家获得了他们原本买不起的游戏。</p><p>其他消息方面，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/amazon">亚马逊</a>的<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/fallout"><em>《辐射》</em></a>电视剧将在 4 月 11 日的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/amazon-prime-video">Prime 会员</a>中放弃所有剧集，但<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/fallout-tv-shows-first-episode-will-be-streamable-on-twitch-3615292">人们也可以在 Twitch 上免费观看第一集</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/game-staff-reportedly-told-to-expect-redundancies-3615320">据报道，GAME 工作人员被告知预计裁员的消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
